{"tid":840253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"烏克蘭軍隊安全系統密碼被踢爆 密碼：123456","createTime":"2018-09-28T14:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T15:46:17.000Z","uid":28765,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e2e593dc9de3161b1a9ea3a8bc2885eb3b55e95b","tid":840253,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T14:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LlWNoV6ssBDg1wXO5Fj2xg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9MzE1/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/pc3mag.com/fedf46d631d2fb8d370867a5af6d2862\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FLlWNoV6ssBDg1wXO5Fj2xg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9MzE1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fpc3mag.com%2Ffedf46d631d2fb8d370867a5af6d2862&h=4791f2fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「admin」和「123456」是世界上最常見的帳號密碼組合，不少路由器的預設帳號會用它，但你可能想不到，這種危險帳號密碼組合會在軍隊出現。<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭記者 Alexander Dubinsky 最近發現烏克蘭軍隊的「第聶伯羅」自動化控制系統的帳號資料，從中發現帳號名稱竟然是「admin」，密碼是「123456」。利用這帳號資料，所有人都可以登入烏克蘭軍隊的路由器、伺服器等等可連接網絡的裝置。如果其他國家知道烏克蘭軍隊密碼原來是這麼簡單的話，烏克蘭軍隊的機密盪然無存。<br />\n<br />\n上年有系統保安公司 Keeper Security 的密碼管理團隊發現世界上最多人使用的密碼是「123456」和「123456789」，因此「123456」作為一個密碼非常危險。在當地記者揭發之後，烏克蘭軍隊已經修改密碼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E8%BB%8D%E9%9A%8A%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC%E8%A2%AB%E8%B8%A2%E7%88%86-%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC-123456-100003773.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2583%258F%25E5%2585%258B%25E8%2598%25AD%25E8%25BB%258D%25E9%259A%258A%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%25AF%2586%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E7%2588%2586-%25E5%25AF%2586%25E7%25A2%25BC-123456-100003773.html&d=3CIn%2BtRdungA6zKxfN3KmywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=8d0c9782\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E8%BB%8D%E9%9A%8A%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC%E8%A2%AB%E8%B8%A2%E7%88%86-%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC-123456-100003773.html</a>"},{"pid":"1afa460852334623e1bc8c93663a013073e7ecd4","tid":840253,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T14:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4913d6dc152aea44fb93f461fd90d89d766ede00","tid":840253,"uid":29080,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T14:47:24.000Z","msg":"密碼係個心"},{"pid":"148abd9cb1a7187ac6601baa7248e755d4f9c825","tid":840253,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"講開又講<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭內戰打完未?? 家陣東部是否依然被 親俄叛軍控制??"},{"pid":"67d9528250b5ee0c0cbb037141cee7ac69af8b29","tid":840253,"uid":2949,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:03:37.000Z","msg":"最危險=最安全"},{"pid":"0248d0f31649e5b66a20307952f841c32386a3a8","tid":840253,"uid":165773,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:07:35.000Z","msg":"fake你ga<br />\n你打非正式密碼都會成功login<br />\n但係係特設既裝假狗page<br />\n同時監視你入去想做咩手"},{"pid":"3c739800420494272a66ad6e74024b7fde799436","tid":840253,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"148abd9cb1a7187ac6601baa7248e755d4f9c825","tid":840253,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"講開又講<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭內戰打完未?? 家陣東部是否依然被 親俄叛軍控制??"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:07:36.000Z","msg":"暫時休戰<br />\n<br />\n英國出左聲話係內戰未完前, 會支持烏克蘭打落去<br />\n目測歐美既支援已經到緊去烏克蘭"},{"pid":"f77cc94e1761ae8c9a537740b05423e8a7fdd122","tid":840253,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c739800420494272a66ad6e74024b7fde799436","tid":840253,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"148abd9cb1a7187ac6601baa7248e755d4f9c825","tid":840253,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"講開又講<br